China's not getting rich
burning coal on the blue path.

00:33:13.770 --> 00:33:18.450
We're not increasing our
energy at all probably.

00:33:18.450 --> 00:33:20.340
Europe is cutting
back even farther

00:33:20.340 --> 00:33:21.960
to get to that blue path.

00:33:21.960 --> 00:33:25.190
That's a big deal.

00:33:25.190 --> 00:33:26.720
So if it's the
easiest thing to do

00:33:26.720 --> 00:33:29.750
and it's an important thing
to do, it's a big deal.

00:33:29.750 --> 00:33:32.810
So that's one reason
why it's hard is

00:33:32.810 --> 00:33:34.860
we live on fossil fuels.

00:33:34.860 --> 00:33:37.910
So if you're going to cut
the use of fossil fuels,

00:33:37.910 --> 00:33:40.140
emissions from fossil fuels--

00:33:40.140 --> 00:33:42.800
it's emissions
from fossil fuels--

00:33:42.800 --> 00:33:44.240
you could do some
fuel switching.

00:33:44.240 --> 00:33:45.460
You can do some efficiency.

00:33:45.460 --> 00:33:47.210
You can do some this,
that, and the other.

00:33:47.210 --> 00:33:50.330
But you will have to do a lot.

00:33:50.330 --> 00:33:52.110
New technologies
will be essential.

00:33:52.110 --> 00:33:54.080
But they may or may
not appear in time.

00:33:56.620 --> 00:33:59.220
OK, so that's a big deal.

00:33:59.220 --> 00:34:00.610
So we all go to bicycles.

00:34:00.610 --> 00:34:02.440
That's great.

00:34:02.440 --> 00:34:03.690
We can do that.

00:34:03.690 --> 00:34:04.890
We can emulate the Dutch.

00:34:04.890 --> 00:34:08.179
And we can all bicycle to work.

00:34:08.179 --> 00:34:09.305
But we're not the problem.

