agreement in place.

00:57:14.110 --> 00:57:19.673
What happened in Doha, and it's
on my slides for Wednesday,

00:57:19.673 --> 00:57:20.590
but I'll tell you now.

00:57:20.590 --> 00:57:24.160
What happened in
Doha was basically

00:57:24.160 --> 00:57:27.960
the Europeans
