to go from the rich countries

00:57:31.890 --> 00:57:34.080
to the poor countries,
a much smaller promise

00:57:34.080 --> 00:57:36.460
than you will consider
Wednesday and Friday.

00:57:36.460 --> 00:57:38.160
But there was a promise.

00:57:38.160 --> 00:57:40.830
We'll see if it's kept.

00:57:40.830 --> 00:57:45.230
And the developing
world promised

00:57:45.230 --> 00:57:48.080
to consider making promises.

00:57:48.080 --> 00:57:50.780
That is to say the
refusal to commit ever

00:57:50.780 --> 00:57:52.910
