participating in a global regime

00:58:03.220 --> 00:58:08.180
of some sort, not
fully spelled out.

00:58:08.180 --> 00:58:11.330
So the poor countries,
as I say, need

00:58:11.330 --> 00:58:16.830
to participate, have managed
to be excluded so far.

00:58:20.030 --> 00:58:24.410
The task you will face on
Wednesday and Friday is to,

00:58:24.410 --> 00:58:27.920
and I hope do it
with a straight face,

00:58:27.920 --> 00:58:31.370
is to make proposals that have
some hope of being accepted

00:58:31.370 --> 00:58:35.270
when you go back to your
capitals of emissions

00:58:35.270 --> 00:58:38.040
reductions that will get
the job done globally.

