what does that mean we don't do?

01:00:08.010 --> 01:00:10.580
1% of the household
budget, easy.

01:00:10.580 --> 01:00:18.440
But 1% of-- moving 1% of world
GDP from purpose A to purpose B

01:00:18.440 --> 01:00:21.620
requires governments
to do serious things.

01:00:21.620 --> 01:00:23.703
Deciding to cut
back 1% yourself,

01:00:23.703 --> 01:00:24.620
yeah, you can do that.

