01:00:39.650 --> 01:00:43.190
regulate, do significant things.

01:00:43.190 --> 01:00:45.830
So yeah, it's only 1% of GDP.

01:00:45.830 --> 01:00:48.350
And all the models
say that's sort

01:00:48.350 --> 01:00:51.110
