01:04:36.490 --> 01:04:36.990
Yeah.

01:04:36.990 --> 01:04:38.740
AUDIENCE: But it doesn't
specify that they

01:04:38.740 --> 01:04:41.132
have to actually be monitored?

01:04:41.132 --> 01:04:42.840
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE:
Oh, I can't imagine.

