I This country's
got a long history

01:04:46.710 --> 01:04:48.483
of strategic arms reduction.

01:04:48.483 --> 01:04:50.400
Do you remember-- well,
you wouldn't remember.

01:04:50.400 --> 01:04:54.500
But you may have heard
people say trust but verify.

01:04:54.500 --> 01:04:57.080
We've always had that
view internationally.

01:04:57.080 --> 01:04:58.940
We want to make sure
if we're going to obey,

01:04:58.940 --> 01:05:00.920
we're going to make sure
