They're getting investment,
why would they not want to?

01:09:50.190 --> 01:09:51.990
Besides the
measurement problem, I

01:09:51.990 --> 01:09:53.930
would see it as someone
who's trying to get

01:09:53.930 --> 01:09:55.082
foreign investment anyway.

