We want to get rich.

01:10:04.797 --> 01:10:06.380
You guys got rich
burning fossil fuel.

01:10:06.380 --> 01:10:08.510
And you're telling us--

01:10:08.510 --> 01:10:10.310
I assume I'm going to
hear a bunch of this

01:10:10.310 --> 01:10:13.160
on Wednesday and Friday
from the developing world.

